WEBVTT

00:48.715 --> 00:51.384
Does she know that you're being so lame?

00:52.302 --> 00:54.721
Lame? What are you talking about?

00:56.473 --> 00:57.348
Wait.

00:57.807 --> 00:59.350
You must be really into her.

00:59.601 --> 01:01.770
He seems so desperate.

01:02.228 --> 01:03.063
Stop it.

01:03.813 --> 01:05.940
Let's talk about something else.

01:06.691 --> 01:10.779
Anyhow, that means
nothing is for certain yet.

01:11.863 --> 01:12.739
Aren't I right?

01:14.991 --> 01:16.242
Well,

01:20.288 --> 01:21.915
not just yet...

01:32.842 --> 01:34.844
Why are you hiccupping?
Are you drunk already?

01:35.720 --> 01:36.721
No, I'm not.

01:37.472 --> 01:38.473
That's weird.

01:39.808 --> 01:41.392
Cheers, everyone.

01:41.476 --> 01:44.020
- Cheers. Nice to meet you.
- Cheers.

01:52.195 --> 01:54.656
Are hiccups contagious too?

02:14.509 --> 02:17.804
You said you live in Mok-dong, right?
I live in Hwagok-dong. I'll drop you off.

02:18.096 --> 02:20.932
Oh, you don't have to.

02:21.015 --> 02:22.559
Don't worry, it's a short detour.

02:23.226 --> 02:24.686
Good for you.

02:26.146 --> 02:28.982
You should ask him for a ride today.

02:29.065 --> 02:30.817
I left my bag at the office.

02:31.526 --> 02:32.819
So did I.

02:32.902 --> 02:36.364
You're going home, not to school.
What do you need a bag for?

02:36.447 --> 02:37.657
There's something I need in it.

02:37.740 --> 02:40.201
Do I have to take care of him again?

02:42.704 --> 02:44.747
Where do you live, Ms. Yoon?

02:45.874 --> 02:48.293
I live in Bundang.

02:49.002 --> 02:50.962
You can come with us, then.

02:51.546 --> 02:53.590
We can drop you off after Seung-cheol.

02:54.007 --> 02:55.174
Sure.

02:56.175 --> 02:57.635
Oh, I forgot.

02:59.304 --> 03:01.681
There's something my sister told me
to give you in my car.

03:02.181 --> 03:03.558
Oh, that.

03:03.641 --> 03:07.353
I was wondering when I could get it
since I don't visit the office often.

03:07.437 --> 03:10.231
- You should take it right now.
- I should.

03:10.815 --> 03:11.649
Right.

03:12.650 --> 03:13.693
Let's get going.

03:27.123 --> 03:27.957
Oh, gosh.

03:32.754 --> 03:33.838
Why did you hold my hand?

03:36.716 --> 03:38.134
Because it was there.

03:39.344 --> 03:41.221
Why? Did you not like it?

03:42.639 --> 03:43.640
It's not that.

03:45.391 --> 03:46.768
You held my hand too.

03:50.271 --> 03:51.564
Why did you hold it first?

03:52.440 --> 03:53.900
I wanted to hold it first.

03:57.403 --> 03:58.696
That would've taken forever.

03:59.656 --> 04:02.617
You have no idea how important
timing is in a relationship.

04:08.206 --> 04:09.707
Are we in a relationship now?

04:12.210 --> 04:14.712
I'm just saying.

04:15.588 --> 04:17.131
Why do you always point things out?

04:17.215 --> 04:19.968
It's like you enjoy putting me
on the spot.

04:21.886 --> 04:23.554
You put me on the spot first.

04:23.846 --> 04:26.224
I became a moron
who can't even make the first move.

04:28.434 --> 04:30.979
I didn't have the heart
to say that myself.

04:31.271 --> 04:32.647
I'm glad you said it yourself.

04:37.443 --> 04:38.444
Where do you want to go?

04:39.320 --> 04:40.738
Should we go get some coffee?

04:41.531 --> 04:43.157
There's an expert
standing in front of you.

04:44.033 --> 04:44.993
That's true.

04:45.994 --> 04:47.161
Let's head over to the office.

04:48.329 --> 04:51.416
But there might be some people
working late.

04:53.334 --> 04:55.420
Not in my office. Let's go.

04:56.129 --> 04:57.088
Okay.

05:21.863 --> 05:22.989
I have work left to do.

05:23.364 --> 05:24.657
I'm here for something else.

05:24.741 --> 05:25.950
I see. Have a good one.

05:26.242 --> 05:27.368
- You too.
- Thank you.

05:57.815 --> 05:58.691
Bye.

06:46.572 --> 06:48.449
Like this? No.

06:59.877 --> 07:01.379
Wait, I need...

07:45.840 --> 07:47.049
I'm here, my friend.

07:47.884 --> 07:49.051
Why are you...

07:51.637 --> 07:53.723
Hey, what are you doing here?

07:54.557 --> 07:55.725
Why are you here?

07:55.892 --> 07:57.685
I'm here for my bag just like you are.

07:57.768 --> 07:59.103
Why did you leave it here?

07:59.187 --> 08:01.397
To be honest,
I figured you might be lonely.

08:01.481 --> 08:03.858
No, get up. Get up and go home.

08:03.941 --> 08:06.444
Why? Do you need to do something?

08:06.569 --> 08:07.403
Do your thing.

08:07.487 --> 08:09.030
- Just wake me up when you go home.
- Gosh.

08:09.697 --> 08:10.656
Wait.

08:12.533 --> 08:14.494
Hey, didn't you hear something?

08:14.577 --> 08:17.163
No, I didn't. It's nothing.

08:20.875 --> 08:22.710
- You little...
- Wait.

08:25.963 --> 08:27.423
My gosh.

08:28.466 --> 08:29.467
Hey.

08:30.593 --> 08:33.888
- Who is that woman you were talking about?
- What?

08:35.056 --> 08:39.143
Who in the world could make you feel
so small and desperate?

08:40.686 --> 08:42.063
What was her name?

08:43.064 --> 08:44.232
Right, So-jeong.

08:44.565 --> 08:46.108
Do you like her more than So-jeong?

08:46.192 --> 08:47.777
What are you talking about? Gosh.

08:47.860 --> 08:49.445
You're being weird, dude.

08:50.112 --> 08:51.948
Stop pretending like you don't know.

08:52.448 --> 08:54.575
Back when you were in the army,

08:54.992 --> 08:59.789
were you or were you not
head over heels for that girl, So-jeong?

09:00.623 --> 09:01.749
You should go.

09:02.250 --> 09:04.335
But I have to admit

09:04.835 --> 09:06.546
that So-jeong was really pretty.

09:06.629 --> 09:08.130
Please, shut up.

09:11.342 --> 09:14.428
Hey, don't you smell coffee?

09:14.512 --> 09:16.472
You must be wasted.

09:16.722 --> 09:18.766
I can't smell coffee.

09:24.438 --> 09:26.399
Wait. The security system.

09:26.482 --> 09:27.942
Just leave it...

09:30.820 --> 09:31.654
It's turned off.

09:47.920 --> 09:48.879
There we go.

09:53.467 --> 09:55.678
Sir, just a moment. Hey, get over here.

09:56.345 --> 09:57.430
Come on.

09:57.555 --> 09:58.764
Let's go.

09:58.848 --> 10:00.141
Let's get you home.

10:00.433 --> 10:01.559
Why aren't you coming?

10:01.642 --> 10:02.643
Get in first.

10:02.977 --> 10:05.104
I told you I need to go somewhere
with my sister.

10:05.646 --> 10:06.981
- You did?
- Yes.

10:07.690 --> 10:08.649
Don't tell me

10:09.191 --> 10:11.819
you're just making me leave
so that you can save money on a taxi.

10:11.902 --> 10:13.070
Take this and leave.

10:13.738 --> 10:15.865
- Here. You can go now, sir.
- Okay.

10:15.948 --> 10:17.491
- Bye.
- Love you, man.

10:17.575 --> 10:18.784
I love you, too. Go.

10:19.869 --> 10:20.703
Go on.

10:32.548 --> 10:34.675
Why didn't you pick up? I was worried.

10:35.217 --> 10:37.094
- Jun-hui.
- Yes?

10:38.554 --> 10:41.223
I'm so scared. When are you coming?

10:41.474 --> 10:43.851
Count to one hundred. No, ten.
I'll be right there.

10:54.820 --> 10:55.821
He's so fast.

11:00.951 --> 11:01.827
Jin-a!

11:04.872 --> 11:05.998
She's not here.

11:10.252 --> 11:11.253
Jin-a.

11:17.760 --> 11:18.803
Where did she go?

11:19.970 --> 11:21.055
Jin-a!

11:25.643 --> 11:27.561
My gosh, seriously?

11:29.605 --> 11:31.232
Gosh, you're so annoying.

11:39.824 --> 11:44.245
I was just playing around.
Why are you so sullen?

11:44.829 --> 11:46.288
I'm not sullen.

11:47.289 --> 11:48.582
Yes, you are.

11:50.626 --> 11:51.836
No coffee for you.

11:52.002 --> 11:52.920
I don't want it.

11:55.005 --> 11:56.090
Fine, then.

11:56.757 --> 11:59.635
Oh, I might eat lunch
with Seung-cheol tomorrow.

11:59.718 --> 12:00.553
Do you want to join?

12:01.220 --> 12:02.721
Why would you eat with him?

12:03.764 --> 12:04.932
To find more about So-jeong.

12:06.225 --> 12:08.102
It... It was nothing serious.

12:22.116 --> 12:24.201
I said, stay seated.

12:27.872 --> 12:30.207
It's really nothing.

12:33.085 --> 12:36.130
I guess you're different
because you are an art major.

12:36.630 --> 12:38.924
You were being so dramatic
over a casual relationship.

12:40.551 --> 12:42.261
How sensitive of you.

12:45.723 --> 12:48.392
Everyone has a past of their own.
And plus,

12:49.018 --> 12:50.811
you're the one who told me

12:51.103 --> 12:53.189
that people become crazy
when they're in love.

12:53.772 --> 12:55.191
You said passion is necessary.

12:56.233 --> 12:58.861
Without it, you said
it would be disrespectful to the other.

12:59.361 --> 13:00.654
Did you say that or not?

13:00.738 --> 13:03.532
You memorized what I told you
word-for-word.

13:04.909 --> 13:07.953
Of course. I'm a sensitive guy.

13:17.254 --> 13:19.882
Come here. I'll show you something.

13:20.007 --> 13:20.883
What?

15:51.659 --> 15:52.534
Hey.

15:53.369 --> 15:55.079
Did you get home already?

15:55.996 --> 15:57.039
"Already"?

15:57.122 --> 15:59.083
I got home a while ago
and washed up to call you.

16:00.125 --> 16:02.878
Look. I got changed.

16:08.050 --> 16:11.553
I think beer definitely tastes better
right after you get out of the shower.

17:14.408 --> 17:15.951
You should have woken me up.

17:16.535 --> 17:19.413
You always wake up to the alarm.

17:19.496 --> 17:22.082
I thought you were going
to work late today.

17:26.295 --> 17:27.379
I'll borrow your car.

17:28.338 --> 17:29.465
Drive safely.

17:30.132 --> 17:32.384
Did she forget to set the alarm
before going to bed?

17:34.511 --> 17:37.139
It sounded like she was on the phone
until late at night.

17:38.348 --> 17:40.392
With whom? Do you think it was a guy?

17:41.226 --> 17:42.436
Who knows?

17:43.270 --> 17:45.856
Don't pry. Just leave her alone.

17:55.324 --> 17:56.992
Are we having injeolmi for breakfast?

17:57.659 --> 17:59.369
Why can't we have soup?

17:59.620 --> 18:01.246
Did you drink again without telling me?

18:02.498 --> 18:03.373
No.

18:03.457 --> 18:06.251
I highly doubt that.

18:07.127 --> 18:08.587
You're half responsible

18:08.670 --> 18:11.006
for Jin-a and Gyu-min drifting apart.

18:12.174 --> 18:13.926
What? Am I wrong?

18:14.009 --> 18:15.677
We may not be as well off as the in-laws.

18:15.928 --> 18:17.763
But we should've proven ourselves
to some extent

18:17.846 --> 18:20.182
so that they wouldn't think
Jin-a is not good enough for him.

18:21.141 --> 18:22.559
Was I unemployed all along?

18:23.102 --> 18:25.479
I had worked for more than 30 years.

18:25.562 --> 18:27.231
Isn't that what all fathers do?

18:27.314 --> 18:29.108
The father has to have a decent job

18:29.191 --> 18:32.361
for the children to have confidence
to do anything.

18:34.571 --> 18:37.407
Think about how you spend your days
these days.

18:41.995 --> 18:43.205
Gosh.

18:43.747 --> 18:45.916
Gosh, I'm so sick of this.

19:01.682 --> 19:02.724
Hi.

19:03.976 --> 19:04.810
Me?

19:05.561 --> 19:07.146
I'm leaving now. Why?

19:10.440 --> 19:11.984
You're almost here?

19:13.193 --> 19:16.280
I see. No, I'm still home.

19:16.655 --> 19:18.490
I'm just heading downstairs.

19:19.158 --> 19:20.742
Okay, great.

20:35.275 --> 20:38.320
You should have called first.
What if we missed each other?

20:38.570 --> 20:41.073
Your phone was turned off,
so I couldn't call you.

20:41.240 --> 20:42.491
It was out of battery.

20:43.242 --> 20:44.326
Right.

20:46.245 --> 20:48.288
Anyway, did you just come down
from your house?

20:49.039 --> 20:49.873
Of course.

20:54.795 --> 20:55.963
What's so funny...

20:57.422 --> 20:58.840
Were you watching all along?

20:59.716 --> 21:01.343
Not from the beginning.

21:02.135 --> 21:03.470
After I hung up, I happened to...

21:03.845 --> 21:05.639
You were great at backing your car.

21:05.722 --> 21:07.266
Were you that eager to see me?

21:07.349 --> 21:09.476
- Just unlock the door.
- It's already unlocked.

21:20.654 --> 21:22.656
How can you be so cute?

21:22.906 --> 21:24.241
Quit it.

21:25.659 --> 21:28.453
Will I be able to see that again
if I pick you up every day?

21:28.704 --> 21:30.080
I said, quit it.

21:30.872 --> 21:33.917
Why? You looked so cute, you know.

21:37.421 --> 21:38.547
Really?

21:39.131 --> 21:40.382
Did you believe that?

21:40.590 --> 21:41.717
Let go.

21:42.801 --> 21:44.928
I'll never let go.
It took me ages to hold your hand.

21:50.559 --> 21:51.560
Anyhow,

21:52.686 --> 21:54.396
do you think it'll be okay?

21:56.398 --> 21:57.566
It has to be.

22:00.527 --> 22:01.653
Aren't you scared?

22:03.905 --> 22:05.198
We are not committing a crime.

22:05.824 --> 22:07.617
Don't worry about anything right now.

22:08.285 --> 22:09.828
We can settle it when something happens.

22:13.540 --> 22:14.916
You're pretty reliable.

22:17.919 --> 22:19.588
You are so into me.

22:32.684 --> 22:35.604
Mr. Kong. About the Dangjin store...

22:36.521 --> 22:37.939
Do it properly.

22:38.023 --> 22:40.358
Don't worry, sir.
We'll make sure to do a good job.

22:42.319 --> 22:43.904
Take your seats for a moment.

22:47.491 --> 22:48.992
Concerning the new store in Dangjin...

22:49.743 --> 22:52.204
The CEO of the mall
as well as the owner of the new store

22:52.287 --> 22:53.955
are Mr. Nam's relatives.

22:54.206 --> 22:57.667
That means they are related to
Mr. Jo as well.

22:59.461 --> 23:01.671
They should feel like
we are paying extra attention to it.

23:02.464 --> 23:03.548
So I'll oversee that place.

23:03.632 --> 23:04.716
I'M NOT GOING THERE!

23:04.800 --> 23:07.677
And I'd like to take
one of our supervisors with me.

23:11.431 --> 23:14.267
I'll be supervising fewer stores
starting next week, so--

23:14.351 --> 23:17.354
If that's the case, you can manage
other stores in your spare time.

23:18.230 --> 23:19.439
Yes, sir.

23:20.774 --> 23:22.484
You should think of it
as a good opportunity.

23:22.567 --> 23:24.069
You should be more open to challenges.

23:24.861 --> 23:27.864
Talk it over and decide.
Ye-eun, bring me the result.

23:27.948 --> 23:28.949
- Yes, sir.
- Dong-u.

23:29.032 --> 23:30.325
Oh, yes, sir.

23:33.370 --> 23:35.330
I have to sit this one out.

23:35.914 --> 23:37.624
I'm never going there.

23:37.707 --> 23:39.918
Well, neither am I.

23:51.721 --> 23:54.057
What do they expect me to do?

24:01.148 --> 24:04.484
Well, does anyone have
spare time next week?

24:04.860 --> 24:07.070
I don't, but I'm not going even if I do.

24:07.529 --> 24:09.573
Especially with Mr. Kong? Never.

24:09.656 --> 24:12.534
Are you kidding me?
You think you can just sit out like that?

24:13.285 --> 24:14.953
We have to discuss it first.

24:15.912 --> 24:18.790
Is that how you initiate a discussion?
Who the hell do you--

24:18.874 --> 24:21.376
You understood quickly since you're smart.

24:21.835 --> 24:24.546
Who the hell do you think you are
to say you're not going?

24:24.963 --> 24:27.924
I hate it so much that I can resign.
That's why I'm not going.

24:28.008 --> 24:29.968
Oh, my. Is that a threat?

24:30.051 --> 24:32.429
There's no need for you two to fight.

24:33.263 --> 24:34.890
I have to go anyway
since I'm the youngest.

24:35.432 --> 24:37.809
I told you not to be submissive
like Jin-a.

24:38.685 --> 24:39.895
I'm not trying to protect you.

24:40.437 --> 24:43.607
It's because people around you
will be denounced as irresponsible.

24:45.483 --> 24:47.527
I'm sorry. Then I'll be honest.

24:48.278 --> 24:50.697
I really don't want to go with Mr. Kong.

24:52.657 --> 24:54.367
It's awful.

24:55.869 --> 24:57.454
Long time no see.

24:58.038 --> 24:59.831
- Hello.
- Hi.

24:59.915 --> 25:02.000
Here comes the lucky person.

25:02.083 --> 25:04.544
What? Why am I the lucky person?

25:07.589 --> 25:08.590
Ms. Yoon.

25:08.673 --> 25:10.300
BUSINESS TRIP TO DANGJIN

25:10.383 --> 25:11.885
"Business trip to Dangjin."

25:15.597 --> 25:17.933
I know you're all busy
for having to oversee my stores.

25:18.016 --> 25:20.310
I would go if I didn't have to work
at the Gasan store.

25:20.393 --> 25:22.270
- But I don't want to burden anyone.
- No.

25:22.395 --> 25:23.563
You're not burdening anyone.

25:23.647 --> 25:26.608
Overseeing one more store
for a day isn't a big deal.

25:27.609 --> 25:28.652
Don't you agree, Ye-eun?

25:29.236 --> 25:30.487
Well, yes.

25:31.196 --> 25:34.824
Really? Then one of you can take my place
for a day, and I'll go.

25:35.116 --> 25:36.576
You just said you'll go.

25:36.910 --> 25:39.871
- It's settled now.
- Okay, I'll go.

25:39.955 --> 25:42.123
Then I'll take your place
at the Gasan store.

25:42.791 --> 25:43.792
Thank you.

25:44.918 --> 25:46.836
- I'm going to go now.
- Okay.

25:46.920 --> 25:50.257
I have a meeting. Good luck, Jin-a.

25:50.674 --> 25:52.175
We'll cover for you.

25:57.389 --> 26:00.183
I'm sorry.
I really shouldn't do this to you.

26:00.934 --> 26:02.644
Why are you sorry?

26:04.020 --> 26:06.439
The business trip to Dangjin
is for two days.

26:07.482 --> 26:09.109
And you need to go with Mr. Kong.

26:09.776 --> 26:12.070
- What?
- I'm sorry.

26:13.154 --> 26:16.616
A business trip? To where? Can I come too?

26:17.200 --> 26:20.620
Of course not.
Plus, I'll be gone for two days.

26:21.162 --> 26:22.205
That's nice.

26:23.999 --> 26:27.669
I mean, we can go sightseeing
once you're done with work.

26:27.752 --> 26:28.712
It'll be nice.

26:30.672 --> 26:32.173
I must be out of my mind.

26:32.799 --> 26:34.592
Why did I put myself through this...

26:35.218 --> 26:36.594
I guess you're not going alone.

26:37.679 --> 26:38.722
Are you going with a guy?

26:41.975 --> 26:44.060
Your company is unbelievable.

26:44.144 --> 26:45.687
How could they send you with a guy?

26:47.439 --> 26:48.898
Who's the guy? How old is he?

26:49.691 --> 26:51.526
That's not the problem.

26:51.860 --> 26:54.154
The problem is that he's really annoying.

26:55.238 --> 26:57.073
Are you talking about the pervert?

26:57.574 --> 26:59.451
That guy who touched female employees...

27:04.748 --> 27:06.791
No, don't go.

27:08.585 --> 27:10.462
I don't want to go either.

27:10.545 --> 27:12.797
But I volunteered to go.

27:12.881 --> 27:16.217
I didn't know I'd have to go with him.
No one told me.

27:16.676 --> 27:18.136
I was planning to go with you...

27:25.477 --> 27:26.978
So, you were planning to go with me.

27:29.522 --> 27:31.775
Yes, I was.

27:32.609 --> 27:34.944
But what's the point?
It's not going to happen anyway.

27:35.779 --> 27:37.822
Why do you say that?
We can still go together.

27:41.159 --> 27:43.828
Did you think I'd let you go alone
with that crazy pervert?

27:44.412 --> 27:47.082
What about work?
It's hard for you to take a day off.

27:48.124 --> 27:50.210
If they don't let me take a day off,
I'll just quit.

27:51.878 --> 27:53.213
You're crazy.

27:54.255 --> 27:56.257
I am crazy for someone.

28:15.860 --> 28:17.028
Later today,

28:17.821 --> 28:21.741
I'm going to visit Gyeong-seon
after I drop by a store.

28:21.908 --> 28:24.077
We haven't been meeting that often.
I think she's upset.

28:24.994 --> 28:27.038
She's not upset. She's lovesick.

28:27.288 --> 28:28.998
Okay, I'll be there too.

28:30.166 --> 28:31.209
You too?

28:33.128 --> 28:36.548
Don't you think it'll be awkward
for us to be together around her?

28:37.090 --> 28:38.800
We can enjoy the thrill.

28:38.967 --> 28:40.510
Let's see who can put on a better act.

28:42.220 --> 28:44.013
My gosh, that's absurd.

28:49.769 --> 28:50.979
Do you still have a lot to do?

28:52.647 --> 28:55.692
You can go home first. I need to talk
to the delivery man on the phone.

28:55.775 --> 28:57.235
That won't take long.

28:58.027 --> 29:00.321
You worked hard all day
because I wasn't here.

29:00.905 --> 29:04.325
Don't drink.
Go home early, and get some rest.

29:04.576 --> 29:06.703
- And don't be late tomorrow. Go on.
- Fine.

29:06.786 --> 29:09.581
I'm too scared of you to be tardy.

29:09.664 --> 29:11.875
- I'll see you tomorrow then.
- Okay, bye.

29:21.801 --> 29:23.094
Did you leave something...

29:25.305 --> 29:27.098
How did you know I was here?

29:35.023 --> 29:38.359
Can I have a cup of coffee first?
I'll pay.

29:48.578 --> 29:51.080
You didn't tell me you were coming.
I didn't know you'd come.

29:52.290 --> 29:55.001
Do I need to call?
You're always here anyway.

29:56.336 --> 29:57.670
Were you about to leave?

29:57.837 --> 30:00.173
No, Jin-a said she'd come,

30:00.381 --> 30:02.008
but I can't reach her.

30:04.010 --> 30:05.053
What do you mean?

30:06.221 --> 30:09.390
I thought it was because she's not allowed
to use her phone during work,

30:09.641 --> 30:11.267
but it's way past closing hours now.

30:11.392 --> 30:13.394
She's not picking up nor reading my texts.

30:18.650 --> 30:19.734
Well...

30:20.860 --> 30:24.823
Jin-a, I want to get back together--

30:24.906 --> 30:27.408
No. I told you that I don't want to.

30:28.034 --> 30:30.453
What's wrong with you?
How long are you going to keep this up?

30:30.537 --> 30:32.205
Until you come back to me.

30:34.082 --> 30:35.041
Listen to me carefully.

30:35.124 --> 30:37.836
You're not doing this because you love me

30:38.127 --> 30:39.462
or have lingering feelings for me.

30:41.047 --> 30:43.675
You are so used to having things your way,

30:43.925 --> 30:47.136
and it's your first time being rejected,
so you're just confused.

30:47.887 --> 30:49.806
You're being stubborn and obstinate.

30:50.139 --> 30:52.016
So what if that's true?

30:52.100 --> 30:54.185
What matters is that I want you back.

30:55.103 --> 30:57.438
That mindset of yours
is already a problem.

30:58.189 --> 31:00.275
I'm not something you can have
when you feel like it.

31:01.192 --> 31:02.861
Don't put on airs.

31:02.944 --> 31:04.779
What's the matter with you?

31:05.363 --> 31:08.241
You graduated from a good school,
and your family's rich.

31:12.245 --> 31:14.873
I'm really sick of this.
Let's not do this anymore.

31:14.956 --> 31:16.958
Please go. I need to close the store.

31:22.380 --> 31:23.965
What's wrong with you?

31:25.884 --> 31:27.135
Oh, gosh.

31:52.160 --> 31:53.745
What the...

31:55.371 --> 31:58.666
You should be ashamed of yourself.
Do you think this will change anything?

32:00.001 --> 32:01.920
Are you trying to show your dominance?

32:02.045 --> 32:04.672
Guys who abuse their strength
are the worst kind ever.

32:04.756 --> 32:07.967
No, nothing's wrong.
I just haven't heard from her today.

32:08.426 --> 32:09.969
You know how close we are.

32:11.346 --> 32:12.347
Okay.

32:13.473 --> 32:15.058
I'm sure she'll call later.

32:15.224 --> 32:17.477
I'll visit you soon, Ms. Kim.

32:17.560 --> 32:19.062
I'm out of kimchi.

32:19.562 --> 32:20.563
Yes.

32:21.522 --> 32:23.900
Yes. Okay, good night.

32:24.651 --> 32:25.693
Bye.

32:27.445 --> 32:31.240
She is not even home. What's going on?

32:31.491 --> 32:32.992
This is driving me crazy.

32:46.214 --> 32:48.091
I didn't know you could be so mean.

32:48.174 --> 32:49.801
This is nothing.

32:51.302 --> 32:54.430
I'm going to report you for sexual assault
if you don't leave now.

32:54.681 --> 32:56.099
I'll just do it right now.

32:57.100 --> 33:01.312
It'd be funny to see our parents
meet each other at a police station.

33:03.773 --> 33:05.149
You just wait.

33:50.778 --> 33:51.696
Jin-a.

33:56.284 --> 33:57.326
Jin-a.

33:58.619 --> 33:59.704
What's all this mess?

34:01.372 --> 34:02.540
What happened here?

34:04.083 --> 34:05.668
- It's nothing.
- What is this?

34:06.210 --> 34:09.005
Who did this? Tell me.

34:12.467 --> 34:14.135
I'm fine.

34:49.587 --> 34:50.797
Here you go.

34:52.006 --> 34:53.132
Oh, thank you.

34:59.806 --> 35:01.474
How can I just leave him be?

35:03.267 --> 35:05.353
How can you say that after what happened?

35:06.062 --> 35:08.815
How do you expect me
to forgive that lunatic?

35:09.357 --> 35:12.068
I don't want to provoke him
and make things worse.

35:12.860 --> 35:13.945
Maybe you're scared.

35:15.530 --> 35:17.490
What are you talking about?

35:20.243 --> 35:21.786
Why are you scared

35:22.453 --> 35:24.080
of a piece of trash like him?

35:27.375 --> 35:29.168
Do you think he's going to stop?

35:30.086 --> 35:31.170
Not at all.

35:31.838 --> 35:33.131
Stay outside.

35:33.881 --> 35:36.217
Don't make things worse.
Just stay outside.

35:47.937 --> 35:49.021
Hey.

35:49.856 --> 35:51.440
Why didn't you call?

35:52.191 --> 35:55.528
You should've called me or the police.
Or even Jun-hui.

35:55.611 --> 35:57.446
Why did you deal with him alone?

35:58.156 --> 36:00.867
I thought he'd leave
if I talked some sense into him.

36:05.079 --> 36:07.790
When has he ever listened to you?

36:08.583 --> 36:10.918
You're always the one being hurt,

36:11.002 --> 36:13.004
and you never know how to fight back.

36:13.379 --> 36:15.381
Being nice isn't something to be proud of.

36:16.007 --> 36:18.217
It's rather a flaw, you idiot!

36:20.303 --> 36:23.806
Don't add on to this.
You're making me upset.

36:24.891 --> 36:26.434
You have no right to cry.

36:31.856 --> 36:32.857
Don't cry.

36:51.959 --> 36:54.587
I know I was a bit harsh on you,
but I didn't mean it.

36:56.672 --> 36:58.424
I know that much.

37:00.885 --> 37:03.262
You should go inside.
Gyeong-seon will be looking for you.

37:04.555 --> 37:07.516
She told me to get lost
and go outside for a walk.

37:07.600 --> 37:09.185
She said she'll clean up.

37:12.939 --> 37:13.981
Are you mad?

37:20.363 --> 37:23.282
I can't do anything about it,
and I shouldn't.

37:23.950 --> 37:25.368
It's only natural that I am mad.

37:27.370 --> 37:28.496
I'm sorry.

37:33.125 --> 37:34.252
What did you do wrong?

37:35.670 --> 37:36.963
You know what I mean.

37:38.589 --> 37:40.591
I made you worry.

37:42.134 --> 37:44.178
I didn't get a chance to call you.

37:48.683 --> 37:49.684
I...

37:52.436 --> 37:54.647
wished that you were with me.

38:06.200 --> 38:09.120
It's just a small scratch.
It doesn't hurt at all.

38:11.122 --> 38:12.999
It hurts me.

38:28.389 --> 38:30.433
I'll never leave you alone from now on.

38:45.740 --> 38:47.074
You should go.

38:49.744 --> 38:51.454
Call me right away if something comes up.

38:52.955 --> 38:53.789
I will.

38:57.335 --> 38:58.336
- Bye.
- Bye

39:04.592 --> 39:06.218
- Bye. Good night.
- Good night.

39:17.813 --> 39:19.357
Do you want to drink?

39:19.815 --> 39:20.983
Should we go to your place?

39:21.400 --> 39:23.986
I'm tired. I want to sleep. Bye.

40:58.622 --> 40:59.915
Is there a bigger one?

41:01.167 --> 41:03.210
You always used this.

41:05.588 --> 41:07.256
I'm not going alone this time.

41:09.091 --> 41:11.302
I'm going with my boss.

41:11.510 --> 41:12.887
It's okay. This will do.

41:16.432 --> 41:17.308
What?

41:18.058 --> 41:20.269
You said you're going on a business trip,

41:20.352 --> 41:23.606
but you've dolled yourself up
with makeup and a nice outfit.

41:24.148 --> 41:26.484
What do you mean?
I put on anything I could find.

41:26.567 --> 41:27.902
Bye.

41:28.777 --> 41:29.862
Be careful.

41:31.155 --> 41:32.239
Okay.

41:41.749 --> 41:43.542
I thought she was going
on a business trip.

41:44.251 --> 41:46.420
Do you think she's being strange as well?

41:47.213 --> 41:50.049
I think she's seeing someone.
Don't you think so?

41:50.549 --> 41:52.885
She has been dressing up lately.

41:53.093 --> 41:55.387
Then I guess she is seeing someone.

41:55.846 --> 41:57.723
I wonder who she's seeing.

41:58.724 --> 41:59.850
Maybe it's Gyu-min.

42:00.226 --> 42:04.438
I knew it. She should never let him go.

42:04.688 --> 42:05.856
You're unbelievable.

42:06.732 --> 42:08.609
He's a scumbag who cheated on Jin-a.

42:08.692 --> 42:11.320
You should be against
them getting back together.

42:11.487 --> 42:14.406
- Aren't you worried about your daughter?
- I was just saying.

42:15.658 --> 42:16.992
My gosh.

42:20.162 --> 42:22.081
Let's get going.

42:24.875 --> 42:26.001
Giddy up!

42:27.378 --> 42:29.630
I'm sure you used to live
in the Joseon Dynasty.

42:29.713 --> 42:30.589
How dare you!

42:31.799 --> 42:33.050
Forgive me, ma'am.

43:05.374 --> 43:06.417
Ms. Jeong.

43:08.919 --> 43:10.212
Did he have to approve something?

43:10.921 --> 43:14.133
It's not that. He wanted to check
on last year's promotional expenses.

43:15.301 --> 43:16.594
Why all of a sudden?

43:17.052 --> 43:18.846
He always checks it
around this time of year.

43:19.471 --> 43:21.974
He hates spending money
on unnecessary things.

43:24.310 --> 43:25.311
That's...

43:26.228 --> 43:27.938
That goes for everyone.

43:28.355 --> 43:30.899
Everyone should think of ways
to cut costs.

43:33.527 --> 43:35.404
I'll think of ways too, sir.

43:46.582 --> 43:49.668
The location of the new store
in Dangjin Shopping Mall

43:50.336 --> 43:51.670
is really great.

43:52.463 --> 43:55.549
The CEO of the mall
and the store owner are my relatives.

43:55.799 --> 43:59.011
So they said they'll work extra harder.

43:59.553 --> 44:01.013
They told me not to worry, sir.

44:02.348 --> 44:05.100
They're getting all the benefits
just because they know someone.

44:05.434 --> 44:07.311
So they'd better do a good job.

44:08.604 --> 44:12.566
We should come up with a way to cut costs.

44:12.650 --> 44:13.817
How about

44:14.443 --> 44:17.863
we train the owners on how to cut costs
on consumable supplies?

44:17.946 --> 44:19.990
I heard Jin-a went on a business trip.

44:20.074 --> 44:23.285
Yes, she did. She went with Mr. Kong.

44:23.369 --> 44:26.163
How lazy are the others
for her to step up and go?

44:26.955 --> 44:29.041
What we need to cut down on
isn't consumables.

44:30.334 --> 44:32.836
It's our employees
who just sit there and do nothing.

44:41.804 --> 44:43.472
- Hello.
- Hello.

44:43.889 --> 44:45.808
Where's your partner?

44:45.891 --> 44:48.977
Oh, Jun-hui? He took the day off
because something came up with his family.

44:49.061 --> 44:49.895
What happened?

44:50.062 --> 44:51.688
I'm not sure.

44:52.940 --> 44:55.609
You seem very curious.

44:57.569 --> 45:01.156
No, I'm not. You guys are always together,

45:01.240 --> 45:03.534
so I just thought you looked
lonely today without him.

45:06.537 --> 45:08.622
This is why I shouldn't spend
too much time with guys.

45:09.123 --> 45:11.667
- I should find a nice girl soon--
- I wish you all the best.

45:11.750 --> 45:13.544
- See you around.
- See you.

45:14.795 --> 45:15.712
Have a good day.

45:15.796 --> 45:17.089
How dare he.

45:17.840 --> 45:19.466
Aren't you interested in Mr. Seo...

45:20.509 --> 45:21.885
Do you think he's out of my league?

45:22.052 --> 45:23.846
No, that's the opposite of what I think.

45:24.263 --> 45:27.724
He looks like a total womanizer.
He seems interested in you.

45:29.101 --> 45:30.436
You think so?

45:30.978 --> 45:32.771
Well, I don't care
even if he's a womanizer.

45:32.855 --> 45:34.523
I can tame him.

45:44.616 --> 45:46.118
Can you stop staring at me like that?

45:46.952 --> 45:47.870
Like how?

45:48.537 --> 45:51.748
You look like a jobless husband
watching his wife getting ready for work.

45:53.167 --> 45:54.751
That sounds pretty nice.

45:54.835 --> 45:55.836
Oops.

45:58.422 --> 45:59.590
You need your shoes.

46:01.633 --> 46:02.634
Thank you.

46:10.350 --> 46:11.393
What are you going to do?

46:11.935 --> 46:13.604
I'll stay right here.

46:13.687 --> 46:16.106
Don't bother me when I work
like you did the other day.

46:16.356 --> 46:19.067
Why don't you do something?
There are many places to see around here.

46:19.651 --> 46:20.903
Doing that alone is no fun.

46:22.738 --> 46:26.909
My absence is too noticeable, isn't it?

46:27.284 --> 46:28.160
Get out.

46:28.744 --> 46:29.828
You never joke with me.

46:30.120 --> 46:31.121
See you later.

46:36.543 --> 46:37.586
Take it easy.

46:37.794 --> 46:38.879
Okay.

46:40.464 --> 46:41.632
Wait just a little while.

46:52.059 --> 46:52.935
What?

47:00.108 --> 47:02.069
What did you say? What?

47:03.195 --> 47:04.488
I said you look pretty!

47:04.571 --> 47:06.907
- Are you crazy? Be quiet.
- What?

47:18.335 --> 47:20.212
- Hello.
- Hello.

47:24.800 --> 47:27.219
It must've been tiring
to drive all the way here.

47:27.803 --> 47:30.806
Well, why did you insist on coming
separately if you were worried about that?

47:32.224 --> 47:36.019
My dad had to be in the area,
so he gave me a ride.

47:36.645 --> 47:38.021
Do a meticulous job, okay?

47:38.647 --> 47:40.899
Mr. Nam's relative is the owner here.

47:41.984 --> 47:43.819
I always follow the protocol.

47:43.902 --> 47:45.612
I'm saying you need to pay
extra attention.

47:48.657 --> 47:49.866
Where are you going, sir?

47:50.492 --> 47:52.327
To say hello
to the CEO of the shopping mall.

47:52.411 --> 47:54.288
The CEO is also Mr. Nam's relative.

47:54.871 --> 47:55.872
He obviously sent me here

47:55.956 --> 47:58.041
so that I can build
a business relationship with them.

48:05.382 --> 48:07.509
- Here you go.
- Thank you.

48:10.012 --> 48:12.347
Here's the schedule
for the orientation session.

48:15.183 --> 48:18.103
Why do you have to gather
all store owners in the country?

48:18.770 --> 48:21.690
That way, you can be acquainted
with each other and exchange information.

48:22.274 --> 48:23.567
You've been to one already.

48:23.734 --> 48:24.943
I know what always happens.

48:25.277 --> 48:27.738
People drink until they drop
and sleep in the next day.

48:28.363 --> 48:30.115
It's a sure way to bond, I guess.

48:32.576 --> 48:35.037
By the way, is something going on
with your family?

48:35.120 --> 48:37.331
My family? No. Why do you ask?

48:40.083 --> 48:42.377
It seems like you really don't want to go,

48:42.461 --> 48:45.172
so I was just wondering
if something came up with your family.

48:46.214 --> 48:49.426
I'm just whining because it feels
like a hassle. My family is fine.

48:51.053 --> 48:53.513
Jin-a said she was going away for work.

48:53.597 --> 48:54.931
Yes, that's right.

49:04.149 --> 49:05.150
Mi-yeon.

49:08.236 --> 49:11.114
Goodness, you're definitely addicted.

49:11.281 --> 49:14.660
Why do you have to exercise twice a day?
My goodness.

49:14.743 --> 49:15.952
It's still not enough.

49:16.036 --> 49:18.622
You should also start exercising
before it gets too late.

49:19.247 --> 49:22.876
I'm just going to
keep on living like this.

49:25.504 --> 49:28.131
I saw Jin-a this morning.

49:28.423 --> 49:30.175
Her boyfriend was driving her to work.

49:31.510 --> 49:33.428
Boyfriend? Where did you see her?

49:34.262 --> 49:36.640
In the parking lot. She was in his car.

49:38.016 --> 49:40.936
She went on a business trip with her boss.

49:41.103 --> 49:44.106
What? But that guy looked very young.

49:45.357 --> 49:47.943
Things are different nowadays, you know.

49:48.026 --> 49:50.112
Even the executives are young.

49:52.739 --> 49:56.993
I see. He was very handsome too.

49:57.869 --> 49:59.871
That's why I just assumed
that he'd be her boyfriend.

50:01.123 --> 50:01.957
Gosh.

50:02.040 --> 50:06.002
I should also buy some fruits
on the way home from my exercise.

50:06.670 --> 50:08.755
- Bye.
- All right.

50:17.305 --> 50:18.306
Are we good to go?

50:18.849 --> 50:21.768
Yes, sir. There are a few things
that need to be fixed,

50:21.852 --> 50:23.937
but I can call
the interior design firm about them.

50:24.020 --> 50:26.022
We'll just have to check
the ingredients tomorrow.

50:26.106 --> 50:27.941
All right. Well...

50:28.400 --> 50:31.194
The CEO and the store owner
would like to have a meal with us,

50:31.278 --> 50:32.738
so just wrap it up.

50:33.071 --> 50:36.616
Well, my stomach is upset.

50:36.742 --> 50:39.286
- I should go back to the hotel--
- What are you talking about?

50:40.120 --> 50:42.330
- I can't digest what I ate earlier--
- Let's go.

50:42.456 --> 50:44.833
I made a reservation
at the best restaurant in the area.

50:44.916 --> 50:48.170
We can just go for noodles.
You really didn't have to do that.

50:48.503 --> 50:52.299
I'm very sorry. My stomach is upset
from what I ate in the morning.

50:52.382 --> 50:55.010
I'll come in early tomorrow
and finish everything.

50:55.093 --> 50:56.386
Thank you for everything today.

50:56.470 --> 50:57.888
Oh, well...

50:58.472 --> 51:02.058
Her stomach is upset.
I'm sorry. Just a moment, please.

51:04.269 --> 51:05.437
Wait, Ms. Yoon!

51:07.814 --> 51:10.734
What the heck are you doing now?
You can't back out like this.

51:12.235 --> 51:13.195
What do you mean, sir?

51:14.613 --> 51:16.490
Come on, you're not usually like this.

51:16.573 --> 51:18.033
You never say no to these things.

51:18.116 --> 51:21.495
"These things"?
What exactly are you referring to?

51:22.037 --> 51:23.413
You know what I'm talking about.

51:24.080 --> 51:27.876
We can eat together
and have a drink as well.

51:28.084 --> 51:30.253
- Then--
- Then play the tambourine at a karaoke bar

51:30.545 --> 51:32.756
and put up with you touching me
inappropriately?

51:37.135 --> 51:38.887
I'm done with those things.

51:39.805 --> 51:41.348
I just can't put up with them anymore.

51:44.059 --> 51:45.310
I'm off, sir.

51:50.899 --> 51:51.817
What's with her?

52:03.119 --> 52:04.120
My gosh!

52:04.579 --> 52:05.580
What's wrong?

52:06.122 --> 52:07.165
Nothing.

52:07.541 --> 52:08.834
Why do you look so surprised?

52:09.376 --> 52:11.086
Why are you here?

52:12.003 --> 52:15.841
I was on the way to the store
because you were taking too long.

52:16.091 --> 52:18.844
Oh, I had things to finish off.

52:19.010 --> 52:20.512
I'm sorry. I kept you waiting too long.

52:20.595 --> 52:22.138
You must be hungry. I'm starving now.

52:22.222 --> 52:24.307
Let's go for some good food, okay?

52:27.811 --> 52:29.437
Just tell me that I dealt with it well.

52:33.275 --> 52:34.317
You handled it well.

52:35.569 --> 52:36.611
Thanks.

55:03.717 --> 55:05.760
I still find it hard to believe...

55:07.762 --> 55:10.306
that we're together like this.

55:15.437 --> 55:16.980
To tell you the truth,

55:19.024 --> 55:20.567
I'm a little worried.

55:22.569 --> 55:24.571
I keep asking myself
if we can really do this.

55:27.949 --> 55:28.950
We can.

55:29.826 --> 55:33.288
I told you.
We can get through it together.

55:38.543 --> 55:39.669
What if...

55:41.921 --> 55:44.382
I regret holding your hand that day

55:45.633 --> 55:47.427
sometime in the future?

55:50.180 --> 55:52.140
Then I'll get so mad at you.

56:00.065 --> 56:03.109
I'll be good to you
so that you'll never regret your decision.

56:04.819 --> 56:05.904
Can I trust you on that?

56:07.739 --> 56:08.740
Yes, you can.

56:10.075 --> 56:11.117
What if I regret?

56:12.452 --> 56:13.578
Then it is what it is.

56:23.046 --> 56:25.340
I know I'll be good to you
because I've regretted so much.

56:26.758 --> 56:28.218
That's why you can trust me.

56:29.469 --> 56:30.553
What did you regret?

56:34.390 --> 56:36.768
Not confessing my feelings to you first

56:38.019 --> 56:39.521
and not holding your hand first.

56:50.573 --> 56:51.699
It's cold.

56:53.493 --> 56:55.787
You should've dressed for the weather
like I did.

56:57.539 --> 57:00.250
Wouldn't most guys offer their jackets
to a lady in this situation?

57:01.167 --> 57:02.252
But I'm cold too.

57:03.711 --> 57:05.338
You're such a jerk.

57:13.555 --> 57:15.473
You fit right in my arms.

57:16.891 --> 57:18.935
You're teasing me again
for being tiny, right?

57:23.731 --> 57:25.316
You can't blame me for this one, okay?

57:26.192 --> 57:27.026
What?

01:03:39.398 --> 01:03:42.693
Good morning. I'll call you after work.

01:03:42.777 --> 01:03:44.028
From the woman in the drawing.

01:04:13.182 --> 01:04:14.559
Don't mind me.

01:04:15.184 --> 01:04:17.562
I told you that I stopped by
for just a cup of coffee.

01:04:17.645 --> 01:04:19.105
The peak hours are over.

01:04:20.690 --> 01:04:23.109
Are things at this store going to change?

01:04:25.194 --> 01:04:28.072
I guess there will be changes
if that's necessary.

01:04:28.906 --> 01:04:30.908
I mean, we all change when we need to.

01:04:34.245 --> 01:04:38.583
Did Ms. Yoon go on that business trip
with a plan to revolt?

01:04:39.000 --> 01:04:40.585
Mr. Kong wants to teach her a lesson.

01:04:41.294 --> 01:04:43.671
- Why?
- I spoke with him on the phone

01:04:43.754 --> 01:04:45.590
- because of a contract for a new store,
- Yes?

01:04:45.882 --> 01:04:49.135
and he went on about how she did things
on her own without consulting him.

01:04:50.928 --> 01:04:52.555
I would've ditched him too.

01:04:55.558 --> 01:04:57.894
But we're talking about Yoon Jin-a here.

01:04:59.896 --> 01:05:01.355
I guess she needed a change.

01:05:08.154 --> 01:05:11.073
I'm fine. You must be tired
from all the driving.

01:05:11.365 --> 01:05:13.576
See? I told you that we should take turns.

01:05:14.744 --> 01:05:17.121
I'm a great driver.

01:05:20.124 --> 01:05:21.125
Next time?

01:05:22.418 --> 01:05:23.836
Are you planning on another getaway?

01:05:26.130 --> 01:05:27.173
I'll call you later.

01:05:28.424 --> 01:05:29.467
Who was that?

01:05:29.717 --> 01:05:32.970
It was Bo-ra. She looked after
the store while I was gone.

01:05:34.680 --> 01:05:36.891
How old is the boss
you went on a business trip with?

01:05:38.017 --> 01:05:40.645
I'm not sure. I guess he is in his 40s.

01:05:41.228 --> 01:05:42.271
Is he handsome?

01:05:42.730 --> 01:05:43.731
What?

01:05:44.523 --> 01:05:47.276
The woman who lives in Unit 704
said that he's very handsome.

01:05:47.526 --> 01:05:49.111
She saw you in his car.

01:05:50.738 --> 01:05:54.200
She must have gotten a glimpse of him
as we were driving.

01:05:55.743 --> 01:06:00.206
She said that she saw you
with a young, good-looking guy.

01:06:00.915 --> 01:06:04.085
Anyway, you should always
watch your behavior.

01:06:04.168 --> 01:06:06.253
Otherwise, you'll be the talk of the town.

01:06:07.588 --> 01:06:10.925
I didn't even do anything.
Why are you scolding me for nothing?

01:06:12.551 --> 01:06:15.721
You and that temper. I was just saying.

01:06:15.805 --> 01:06:16.931
Get out.

01:06:18.099 --> 01:06:20.184
Gyeong-seon will bring Jun-hui tomorrow.

01:06:20.518 --> 01:06:21.519
Why?

01:06:21.769 --> 01:06:24.689
What do you think?
Seung-ho is coming home,

01:06:24.772 --> 01:06:27.316
so it'd be nice for all of us
to gather for a barbecue.

01:06:27.900 --> 01:06:31.362
Besides, we haven't had a chance to invite
Jun-hui for a meal since he got back.

01:06:33.072 --> 01:06:37.034
So what? Gyeong-seon takes
great care of him anyway.

01:06:38.369 --> 01:06:41.831
She's doing her best as his sister.

01:06:42.248 --> 01:06:45.710
They lost their parents
at such young ages,

01:06:45.793 --> 01:06:49.171
so we're used to them being
on their own, but I feel so bad for them.

01:06:49.714 --> 01:06:51.215
Why do you feel bad for them?

01:06:51.298 --> 01:06:52.925
Both of them are doing fine.

01:06:53.009 --> 01:06:54.927
You're so clueless.

01:06:55.553 --> 01:06:58.014
You think they're doing fine?

01:06:58.264 --> 01:07:00.599
Just having a job
doesn't mean that you're doing fine.

01:07:00.683 --> 01:07:04.854
Even if that's the case,
it's just the two of them.

01:07:05.146 --> 01:07:07.440
Think about when they'll get married.

01:07:07.523 --> 01:07:10.192
Let's be honest.
No family will welcome them.

01:07:10.401 --> 01:07:13.070
You're being so mean right now.

01:07:13.237 --> 01:07:15.072
I'm just telling you the truth.

01:07:15.656 --> 01:07:17.658
Just wait and see.
You'll learn that it's true.

01:07:17.742 --> 01:07:21.704
This world isn't an easy place.

01:07:23.789 --> 01:07:25.082
- Mom.
- Yes?

01:07:25.833 --> 01:07:28.127
Don't talk about Gyu-min
in front of them tomorrow.

01:07:28.210 --> 01:07:31.172
Don't bring up anything useless, okay?

01:07:31.338 --> 01:07:33.424
I guess you do have shame, after all.

01:07:33.632 --> 01:07:34.759
You won't, right?

01:07:34.842 --> 01:07:37.094
- Whatever.
- Don't talk about him, okay?

01:07:50.691 --> 01:07:53.027
Yes,
I just heard about it from Gyeong-seon.

01:07:54.987 --> 01:07:56.030
What are you worried about?

01:07:59.617 --> 01:08:01.452
I told you that we have to break taboos.

01:08:03.370 --> 01:08:04.538
I'm not joking right now.

01:08:08.626 --> 01:08:10.044
I told you not to worry ahead.

01:08:10.377 --> 01:08:12.129
We'll worry about it when we need to.

01:08:14.131 --> 01:08:15.674
A mistake? I won't make any mistake.

01:08:29.105 --> 01:08:31.398
- How do you know the passcode?
- What?

01:08:32.733 --> 01:08:35.986
I saw Seung-ho punching in the passcode
a few times when I was with him.

01:08:36.403 --> 01:08:38.280
Why were you watching him
when he was doing that?

01:08:38.531 --> 01:08:39.698
That's rude.

01:08:42.910 --> 01:08:44.370
- Let me pour you a glass.
- Thanks.

01:08:44.453 --> 01:08:46.247
Mr. Yoon, come join us!

01:08:53.045 --> 01:08:54.046
Give me that.

01:08:57.258 --> 01:08:58.717
- Let me pour you one, sir.
- All right.

01:08:58.801 --> 01:08:59.802
You're so sweet.

01:09:02.888 --> 01:09:04.974
Oh, my. It's been a while

01:09:05.266 --> 01:09:07.226
since the entire family
gathered like this.

01:09:07.309 --> 01:09:09.270
Let's clink our glasses before we drink.

01:09:10.020 --> 01:09:12.773
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

01:09:20.156 --> 01:09:22.074
- Thank you for the food.
- Thank you for the food.

01:09:22.158 --> 01:09:23.659
- Thank you for the food.
- Here, Jun-hui.

01:09:33.419 --> 01:09:34.420
Try to relax.

01:09:35.004 --> 01:09:36.881
Why? Am I being awkward?

01:09:36.964 --> 01:09:39.925
Yes, those who are quick-witted
would sense it right away.

01:09:40.009 --> 01:09:42.344
Really? What should I do?

01:09:42.428 --> 01:09:45.431
Just smile. You usually smile a lot.
And you have such a pretty smile.

01:09:53.105 --> 01:09:57.318
I thought all parents
would be like the two of you.

01:09:58.986 --> 01:10:02.865
I definitely thought our dad
would be like you.

01:10:04.825 --> 01:10:09.580
How could he leave us for another woman
in less than half a year after Mom died?

01:10:11.332 --> 01:10:14.501
How could he leave me and Jun-hui behind?

01:10:15.252 --> 01:10:17.254
I can't believe
he abandoned his own children.

01:10:17.880 --> 01:10:19.256
Why are you bringing that up again?

01:10:19.340 --> 01:10:23.177
You have no idea how devastated

01:10:23.302 --> 01:10:25.095
and sad I was back then.

01:10:27.181 --> 01:10:30.226
We had nobody in the whole wide world.

01:10:30.309 --> 01:10:31.852
To be honest,

01:10:33.479 --> 01:10:36.190
I just wanted to die.

01:10:36.899 --> 01:10:39.026
Don't say things like that.

01:10:40.903 --> 01:10:45.115
You have a family right here.
Why are you saying that you have nobody?

01:10:45.449 --> 01:10:46.575
He's right.

01:10:47.284 --> 01:10:49.995
Hearing that hurts my feelings.

01:10:50.579 --> 01:10:53.582
Both of us have always thought

01:10:53.832 --> 01:10:57.127
of you and Jun-hui as our own children.

01:10:57.211 --> 01:10:59.964
I know. Of course, I know that.

01:11:00.172 --> 01:11:04.051
You can call me an ungrateful bitch
if I ever forget about that.

01:11:08.847 --> 01:11:09.848
Stop drinking.

01:11:11.016 --> 01:11:12.476
We already have to put up with her.

01:11:13.227 --> 01:11:14.979
You little...

01:11:15.145 --> 01:11:16.897
You ladies are so old now.

01:11:16.981 --> 01:11:18.357
This happens every time you drink.

01:11:18.857 --> 01:11:19.817
Hey.

01:11:20.985 --> 01:11:22.444
I do admit some part of that.

01:11:23.028 --> 01:11:25.406
But there's nothing wrong with Jin-a.

01:11:25.489 --> 01:11:29.994
Do you even know how many guys
were crazy for her?

01:11:30.077 --> 01:11:31.287
Sure.

01:11:31.370 --> 01:11:33.455
I'm keeping it all to myself now,

01:11:33.539 --> 01:11:36.166
but if I tell you
about her dating history,

01:11:36.250 --> 01:11:38.002
all of you will be so surprised.

01:11:38.085 --> 01:11:40.462
She's drunk. She talks nonsense
every time she gets drunk.

01:11:40.546 --> 01:11:42.506
- Gosh, you.
- No, I'm not drunk.

01:11:43.090 --> 01:11:44.967
- Hey.
- Shall I tell them all about it?

01:11:45.092 --> 01:11:46.927
- I'll--
- You need to stop drinking.

01:11:48.220 --> 01:11:50.931
- You see, Lee Gyu-min--
- Hey.

01:11:51.807 --> 01:11:53.267
What is wrong with you?

01:11:53.809 --> 01:11:55.436
- Stop it.
- What's going on?

01:11:55.894 --> 01:11:57.146
Is Jin-a still seeing that jerk?

01:11:57.229 --> 01:11:58.272
No, I'm not.

01:11:58.647 --> 01:12:00.524
Hey, do you know something?

01:12:01.275 --> 01:12:04.403
No, I don't know anything.
I just wanted to stop her.

01:12:06.030 --> 01:12:06.989
You must know something.

01:12:07.323 --> 01:12:08.741
Just be quiet, will you?

01:12:08.866 --> 01:12:12.953
Hang on. Jin-a, what is going on?

01:12:13.245 --> 01:12:16.415
You told me not to even bring up
Gyu-min's name. Something's up, right?

01:12:16.498 --> 01:12:18.459
That's great news!

01:12:18.542 --> 01:12:21.628
The two of you shouldn't have
broken up so abruptly like that.

01:12:21.712 --> 01:12:22.629
Mom, please.

01:12:22.713 --> 01:12:25.883
Hey, come on. They're our family.

01:12:26.008 --> 01:12:27.593
It's nothing to be embarrassed about.

01:12:27.676 --> 01:12:31.430
All couples break up and get back together
multiple times.

01:12:31.555 --> 01:12:34.016
- Aren't I right?
- No. I'm telling you we are not together.

01:12:34.099 --> 01:12:35.976
I'll never get back together with him.

01:12:37.853 --> 01:12:40.898
Then why were you so head over heels
for him?

01:12:40.981 --> 01:12:43.025
You little... Watch your mouth.

01:12:43.609 --> 01:12:44.860
You're so rude to me.

01:12:44.943 --> 01:12:46.945
Don't hit him on the head.
He needs to study!

01:12:47.029 --> 01:12:50.240
Study, my ass. He needs to become
a decent person first.

01:12:51.367 --> 01:12:52.826
Jin-a is right about that.

01:12:53.410 --> 01:12:57.414
Being a good person is way more important
than getting a PhD.

01:12:58.582 --> 01:12:59.875
I don't care about anything else.

01:13:01.001 --> 01:13:05.047
Before anything else,
one should be considerate of others.

01:13:06.340 --> 01:13:09.927
If Jin-a brings a guy like that,
I'll approve of him in a heartbeat.

01:13:10.010 --> 01:13:11.553
Agreed.

01:13:25.692 --> 01:13:28.404
Hey, what's going on
with that 35-year-old lady?

01:13:29.071 --> 01:13:30.781
Why are you so interested in me
these days?

01:13:31.281 --> 01:13:32.616
I'm not really interested.

01:13:32.991 --> 01:13:35.244
I'm just asking because you looked
so upset the last time.

01:13:35.452 --> 01:13:36.745
I wasn't upset.

01:13:37.037 --> 01:13:39.081
Many guys date older women these days.

01:13:39.164 --> 01:13:41.041
Who knows? You may become one of them.

01:13:41.834 --> 01:13:44.420
I'm not like you.
I don't like older women.

01:13:47.172 --> 01:13:49.425
- Hello?
- You called for a driver, right?

01:13:49.633 --> 01:13:52.344
Oh, yes. It's further in.

01:13:52.428 --> 01:13:54.304
- Okay, I'll be there shortly.
- Thank you.

01:13:54.388 --> 01:13:55.472
The driver is here.

01:13:55.806 --> 01:13:57.850
- All right.
- Go back in. He's almost here.

01:13:59.643 --> 01:14:01.812
Okay. Well...

01:14:02.354 --> 01:14:04.690
Get home safely and call me.

01:14:05.566 --> 01:14:07.568
Let me know
if Gyeong-seon got home safely.

01:14:07.860 --> 01:14:09.736
Okay, I will. Bye.

01:14:09.820 --> 01:14:11.238
- Okay.
- Bye.

01:14:24.126 --> 01:14:26.128
It's chilly today, right?

01:14:26.753 --> 01:14:28.213
What's that talk about Gyu-min?

01:14:28.839 --> 01:14:30.174
It's nothing.

01:14:30.257 --> 01:14:32.801
We got in a hassle when he came again,
and they found out.

01:14:36.472 --> 01:14:38.640
- What?
- From now on, call me when something's up.

01:14:39.641 --> 01:14:41.351
You don't even live close by.

01:14:41.435 --> 01:14:43.520
You are always busy studying.

01:14:43.604 --> 01:14:46.231
And it won't happen again.
We settled everything.

01:14:46.440 --> 01:14:49.109
There's no guarantee
that he will not bother you again.

01:14:50.527 --> 01:14:53.405
Pull yourself together.
You'd better not cause another scene.

01:15:03.582 --> 01:15:04.458
Hold on.

01:15:05.292 --> 01:15:07.586
- Be careful.
- Gosh.

01:15:36.490 --> 01:15:38.075
You switched off the cellular data.

01:15:38.325 --> 01:15:40.202
- What data?
- Turn it on.

01:15:40.410 --> 01:15:42.204
- It is on.
- No.

01:15:42.371 --> 01:15:43.830
Enable cellular data.

01:15:44.331 --> 01:15:45.666
You're an expert.

01:15:46.291 --> 01:15:49.211
- Does this not work if there's no Wi-Fi?
- It should work now.

01:15:49.294 --> 01:15:50.796
Hey, it's not working.

01:15:51.129 --> 01:15:53.298
- Then try this.
- This one?

01:15:53.966 --> 01:15:57.386
- It's working now. You're a genius.
- There you go.

01:16:21.785 --> 01:16:23.537
Yes, it's me.

01:16:49.313 --> 01:16:51.189
I have to go back inside now.

01:16:51.440 --> 01:16:53.191
- What are you doing tomorrow?
- Tomorrow?

01:16:54.610 --> 01:16:57.821
It's my day off, so I'll sleep in.

01:16:58.322 --> 01:17:01.533
I don't have other plans. Why?

01:17:01.700 --> 01:17:03.035
Is there something you want to do?

01:17:03.160 --> 01:17:05.329
Well, not exactly.

01:17:06.246 --> 01:17:07.914
I think there is.

01:17:08.540 --> 01:17:10.375
What is it? Tell me.

01:17:10.667 --> 01:17:11.793
Tomorrow,

01:17:12.836 --> 01:17:16.048
Gyeong-seon is leaving
for an orientation session for two days.

01:17:17.507 --> 01:17:19.926
Do you want to come over?

01:17:45.118 --> 01:17:46.620
Right here is fine.

01:17:52.209 --> 01:17:53.335
Thank you.

01:17:55.337 --> 01:17:56.630
- Have a nice day.
- You too.

01:19:12.914 --> 01:19:13.957
You came.

01:19:15.125 --> 01:19:16.251
You told me to.

01:19:50.952 --> 01:19:52.996
That's very unlike "Ms. Tambourine."

01:19:53.079 --> 01:19:54.331
She's like a different person.

01:19:54.873 --> 01:19:55.749
It's unreal

01:19:55.832 --> 01:19:57.876
that such a pretty lady
is right in front of me.

01:19:59.211 --> 01:20:00.587
Are you crazy? We're at work.

01:20:01.463 --> 01:20:03.632
- Jin-a.
- You want me to make sure that pervert

01:20:03.715 --> 01:20:05.258
won't be able to set foot in the office?

01:20:05.967 --> 01:20:07.844
I think he's dating someone in secret.

01:20:07.928 --> 01:20:10.430
Have you not noticed
something different about him?

01:20:11.681 --> 01:20:12.557
Are you crazy?

01:20:12.641 --> 01:20:14.392
- Can't you stay here tonight?
- Oh, gosh.

01:20:14.476 --> 01:20:16.603
Why didn't you pick up the phone all day?

01:20:16.686 --> 01:20:17.687
You were out of touch.

01:20:18.438 --> 01:20:20.023
How can I ruin this asshole?

01:20:20.774 --> 01:20:22.567
I'll make sure
you never have to hide again.

01:20:23.443 --> 01:20:24.277
I promise.

01:20:29.115 --> 01:20:31.117
Subtitle translation by Choi Hyeon-ju
